@NODE Bugs
@{B}Bugs@{UB}

Previous versions (<43) of sun.datatype didn't always work correct with
picture.datatype 39.14 from Workbench 3.0. When using a HAM8 screen,
sun.datatype reserved 64 colours, but picture.datatype wanted 256 colours. 
@ENDNODE
